@anchor{ratp_hipow}
@deffn {Function} ratp_hipow @
@fname{ratp_hipow} (@var{expr}, @var{x}) @

Finds the highest power of the main variable in @code{ratnumer(expr)}



@c ===beg===
@c load("ratpow")$
@c ratp_hipow( x^(5/2) + x^2 , x) => 2;
@c ratp_hipow( x^(5/2) + x^2 , sqrt(x)) => 5;
@c ===end===
@example
(%i1) load("ratpow")$
@group
(%i2) ratp_hipow( x^(5/2) + x^2 , x) => 2;
incorrect syntax: > is not a prefix operator
(5/2) + x^2 , x) => 
                  ^
@end group
@group
(%i2) ratp_hipow( x^(5/2) + x^2 , sqrt(x)) => 5;
incorrect syntax: > is not a prefix operator
+ x^2 , sqrt(x)) => 
                  ^
@end group
@end example
