@category{Package ratpow}
@closecatbox
@end deffn

@anchor{ratp_lopow}
@deffn {Function} ratp_lopow @
@fname{ratp_lopow} (@var{expr}, @var{x}) @

Finds the lowest power of the main variable in @code{ratnumer(expr)}

@c ===beg===
@c load("ratpow")$
@c ratp_lopow( x^(5/2) + x^3 , x);
@c ===end===
@example
(%i1) load("ratpow")$
@group
(%i2) ratp_lopow( x^(5/2) + x^3 , x);
(%o2)                           0
@end group
@end example

Explanation: The CRE is x^3 + (x^(1/2))^5 * x^0.
