@anchor{ratp_coeffs}
@deffn {Function} ratp_coeffs @
@fname{ratp_coeffs} (@var{expr}, @var{x}) @

Generates a list of powers and coefficients of the main variable
@code{ratnumer(expr)}; returned coefficients are in CRE form except for
numbers.

@c ===beg===
@c load("ratpow")$
@c ratp_coeffs( 4*x^3 + x + sqrt(x), x);
@c ratp_coeffs( 4*x^3 + x + sqrt(x), x);
@c ===end===
@example
(%i1) load("ratpow")$
@group
(%i2) ratp_coeffs( 4*x^3 + x + sqrt(x), x);
(%o2)/R/         [[3, 4], [1, 1], [0, sqrt(x)]]
@end group
@group
(%i3) ratp_coeffs( 4*x^3 + x + sqrt(x), x);
(%o3)/R/         [[3, 4], [1, 1], [0, sqrt(x)]]
@end group
@end example
@opencatbox
@category{Package ratpow}
@closecatbox
@end deffn

